# Golden Context

This body text is compiled verbatim into the provider's root instruction file
(e.g. CLAUDE.md for Claude, GEMINI.md for Gemini, AGENTS.md for Antigravity).

Use `kind: context` to supply workspace-level ambient instructions shared
across all agents — project conventions, coding standards, tool policies, etc.
